{"tid":2298661,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"綠帽天王（美味天王）","createTime":"2020-11-24T08:05:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-24T08:22:41.000Z","uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"36d46091f842be3f3d41bcc67e21b8387f143773","tid":2298661,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T08:05:14.000Z","msg":"咁大間嘅？ 哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈 <br />\nNumber 1呀~ 點解咁好住架? <br />\n正到痺呀! 好好嘆呀! 冇得頂呀!<br />\n<br />\n平平淡淡日日亦都慣 想玩PS5每一天 <br />\n即使意興闌珊也罷 住係別墅會漸覺開懷 <br />\n無謂日日夜夜感嘆 幾多哀傷暫時忘了吧 <br />\n天天也有綠帽送別<br />\n如若你會氹下我 我或會買票登過Taiwan <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打一齊改落去，呢一年綠帽佳簡直係我偶像，殺人犯重可以告埋人地老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e561574dc3004fb03eba569bc5a8cfd90db6bb0","tid":2298661,"uid":137038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T08:20:09.000Z","msg":"呢首已經係野味天王<br />\n改過第二首啦"},{"pid":"b57997f9915ada8bc660c699174c129114f4e727","tid":2298661,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e561574dc3004fb03eba569bc5a8cfd90db6bb0","tid":2298661,"uid":137038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T08:20:09.000Z","msg":"呢首已經係野味天王<br />\n改過第二首啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T08:22:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}